# ── Map provider (frontend) ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Mapbox public token (pk.…). Used for map tiles, geocoding, and route lines.
# Get one at https://account.mapbox.com/access-tokens/ and restrict it to your
# domain (URL restriction). Leave empty to fall back to the free OSM/OSRM stack
# (dev only — rate-limited, not for production).
VITE_MAPBOX_TOKEN=
